{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"viewForAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view that requested the annotation view."}]}]},{"name":"annotation","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The object representing the annotation that is about to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The view object to display for the given annotation or ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to display an annotation image instead.","type":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Implement this method to mark a point annotation with a view object. If you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to mark a particular point annotation with a static image instead, omit","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method or have it return ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" for that annotation, then implement","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:imageForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Annotation views are compatible with UIKit, Core Animation, and other Cocoa","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Touch frameworks. On the other hand, static annotation images use less memory","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and draw more quickly than annotation views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The user location annotation view can also be customized via this method. When","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"annotation"},{"text":" is an instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true},{"text":" (or equal to the map view’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"text":" property), return an instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(or a subclass thereof).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Related examples","type":"heading","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images, learn how to specify what","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to use for a given ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object on your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L753"},"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:viewForAnnotation:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"View representing an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" on screen."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNUserLocation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property of the map view displayed in your application."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapViewDelegate"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","title":"MLNMapView"}}}